                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18150111-138-off788" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150111-138-off788" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150111-138-off788" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150111-138-cd789" type="crimeDate">15th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150111-138-off788 t18150111-138-cd789"></join>, fifteen pound weight of whipcord. value 3 l. nine dozen of harness buckles, value 11 s. 3 d. and four balls of sewing hemp, value 11 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150111-138-victim1136" type="victimName">
